## Fresh-Session Test

Use this to check whether the harness is useful to a new agent.

| Question | Current Answer Source | Gap Or Action |
| --- | --- | --- |
| What is this system or package? | README, root instructions, or project docs | REVIEW REQUIRED |
| How is the repo organized? | component inventory, architecture docs, module docs | REVIEW REQUIRED |
| How does it start? | init entrypoint, package scripts, dev docs | REVIEW REQUIRED |
| How is it verified? | verification matrix, sensor registry, CI docs | REVIEW REQUIRED |
| What work is current? | progress, handoff, feature list, roadmap, issue tracker | REVIEW REQUIRED |

