## Completion Evidence Ladder

| Evidence Layer | Use When | Example Evidence |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Static | Any code, docs-link, config, or template change | lint, type check, compile, schema validation, docs link check |
| Runtime/startup | The app, package, service, CLI, or tool must start or execute | startup command, smoke test, local command run, health check |
| System/user flow | A change crosses components or affects user-visible behavior | end-to-end flow, integration scenario, benchmark slice, screenshot or trace |

Skipping a required layer means the item is not complete. Record reason, risk,
and next best evidence when a layer cannot run.

